				<div id="text-8" class="widget widget_text"><h3 class="widget-title">Contacto</h3>			<div class="textwidget"><p><strong>Andrés Manuel López Obrador</strong></p>
<p><em>Presidente de México</em></p>
<p><strong>t. 5093 4900</strong></p>
